{"tid":97271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鬼國地獄港人內地做和事老反被圍毆 頭面受傷縫30針","createTime":"2017-01-27T14:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T06:29:08.000Z","uid":22736,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7974fca0f21107fdbfca93a36a7e7f74d7b0fc71","tid":97271,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:04:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170127&amp;guid=56231286&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170127%26guid%3D56231286%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=eWF3JVrZtYO%2BsRPnNlRqMJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=bd1c68bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170127%26guid%3D56231286%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=8cb2f6d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170127&amp;guid=56231286&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n港人回鄉度歲，疑因做和事老慘變出氣沙包，頭爆需縫逾30針！讀者黃小姐稱，其60歲父親與24歲胞弟，前晚一同返回廣東汕尾海豐縣梅隴鎮，並搭乘一輛三輪車擬返鄉間與鄉親共度新歲，其間遭多人圍毆受傷。<br />\n<br />\n黃小姐引述家人講出經過，前晚8時許，父親與胞弟的車輛將抵達鄉親住所時，疑因車輛急煞導致尾隨電單車收掣不及相撞。電單車車上3名男子落車，「佢哋將三輪車司機拉落車狂毆，之後阿爸唔想搞到過唔到年，諗住好心做和事老，點知就畀班人打到瞓晒地，圍住嚟狂踢，佢成60歲，根本招架唔到，仲要畀人用硬物扑頭。」<br />\n<br />\n黃小姐續稱，其胞弟阻止時亦被人圍毆，「佢都俾人打到頭破血流」，事後，兩父子負傷返回鄉親家中，由親友協助送院敷治，父親的傷口需縫逾30針，胞弟則傷及眼角及後腦，至少需縫7針，事後有報警。據悉，對方亦有人受傷，醫院門外一度聚集近100人，家人恐出事，遂安排轉到另一間醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n黃小姐昨晚趕抵當地醫院，亦見有公安到場錄取口供。相隔半小時後，一名相信是對方的「大哥」到場，「佢哋想私了件事，係咁塞600蚊畀我阿爸，話『多一事不如少一事，就當我哋唔著啦』等等。」黃小姐稱，這兩天家人的醫藥費已需逾萬元，不能私了了事。據黃小姐所知，對方是一班當地青年會成員，「聽講好多人都飲咗酒。」<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/27/220437_6f6939f269c0793532ee67e4f00182af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F27%2F220437_6f6939f269c0793532ee67e4f00182af.jpg&h=19bc3425&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30632c57df39592044f02f45cc2dd371c241966a","tid":97271,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:06:00.000Z","msg":"包容下啦"},{"pid":"5892f7f8a7f7b217ff304574a89600b91bcf1a9a","tid":97271,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:11:24.000Z","msg":"屌你老母海豐啲撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n番緊大陸拜山都覺得依班仆街唔係人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e04a5a652ace96e6b9e173aee9a27ac2d79811","tid":97271,"uid":27575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:12:36.000Z","msg":"六百蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e835a8fce35db102f6640f40be0684d6139ae130","tid":97271,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:14:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母海豐啲撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n番緊大陸拜山都覺得依班仆街唔係人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前仲有人成日吹捧 呢D撚話<br />\n話咩「天上怕雷公, 地下海陸豐」<br />\n<br />\n實際上只係講緊佢地係一班野蠻人, 人人都怕左佢地<br />\n 都唔知有乜好吹捧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b515d9926bc48a1ccddc0fa264ec594a1ec61d1","tid":97271,"uid":49228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:17:23.000Z","msg":"蚹蛤蟈蜻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb523996c511c45750e3db0e59e62871d039c7d8","tid":97271,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:21:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你老母海豐啲撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n番緊大陸拜山都覺得依班仆街唔係人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前仲有人成日吹捧 呢D撚話<br />\n話咩「天上怕雷公, 地下海陸豐」<br />\n<br />\n實際上只係講緊佢